# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# The standalone legal pages were folded into the About tab of index.html
# (each is now a path-routed entry). Preserve old inbound links — e.g. the
# privacy-policy URL registered on the Steam store — so they don't 404.
#
# Deep paths like /about/privacy or /features/endless are NOT listed here: they
# are handled by Cloudflare Pages' default single-page-application fallback
# (active because the build ships no 404.html), which serves index.html for
# unmatched paths while still serving real assets (/css, /js, /images) directly.
# Do NOT add a "/* /index.html 200" catch-all — _redirects rules are applied
# even when an asset matches, so a catch-all would shadow those assets.
/credits.html   /about/credits   301
/privacy.html   /about/privacy   301
/health.html    /about/health    301
